iographic+features+of+biliary+strictures+after+liver+transplantation+for+primary+sclerosing+cholangitis%3A+evidence+of+recurrent+disease&amp;author=R+Sheng&amp;author=WL+Campbell&amp;author=AB+Zajko&amp;author=RL+Baron&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=1109-1113&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.166.5.8615253&amp;pmid=8615253">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section></div><div class="core-collateral" role="dialog" aria-modal="true"><div id="core-collateral-info" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>Information &amp; Authors</h2></header><section id="tab-information" role="tabpanel"><h3>Information</h3><section class="core-self-citation"><h4>Published In</h4><div class="core-journal-presentation">



        
